features: GENTLE COMFORT: Quality without compromise! Believe Baby Diapers are made from the softest, all-natural materials responsibly sourced from Mother Earth. These biodegradable disposable diapers feature a soft elastic leg and waistband, secure hook and loop tabs that won't stick to skin, and a comfortable belly button cutout to avoid irritation, offering the best for your newborn and the environment.

HYPOALLERGENIC: Unscented and free from harmful chemicals, preservatives, and additives! Believe Baby Diapers have NO chlorine, latex, alcohol, TBT, PVCs, lotions, fragrances, or phthalates. Just sustainable, skin-friendly materials found in nature.

SUPER-ABSORBENT: Naturally wicks moisture away! The super-absorbent bamboo fiber and chlorine-free pulp made from US virgin wood pull wetness away from your baby's skin and absorbs liquid without leaking. Always know when it's time for a change with the vertical blue stripe wetness indicator.

SUSTAINABLE & ECO FRIENDLY: When you nurture your baby, you nurture the world! Believe Baby Diapers are made with sustainably harvested bamboo and natural, plant-based materials. The result is a soft, super-absorbent biodegradable diaper that is gentle on baby's sensitive skin and friendly to Mother Earth.

BELIEVE BABY: Committed to making a great diaper for babies and the planet while helping those who need it most, we Believe a little change can do a lot of good! With every one of our sustainable, earth-friendly diapers you buy, we'll donate a Believe Baby Diaper to a US family in need through our 1-to-1 matching program.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Absorbent, soft, quality diapers.
reviews.reviewText: I’m obsessed with coterie diapers but I wanted to try one of the top cleanest diapers and this wa son the list. These are super soft. Absorbent compared to the other clean diapers I’ve tried! The material feels nice and durable for how clean they are. Love them

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Needs to be packaged in a box when sending.
reviews.reviewText: Great diapers….But can you package them in a box 📦???? It’s very unprofessional and the package around the diapers gets dirty.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I ordered these because they were the “cleanest” brand I could get in the shortest time. Very soft, but not as absorbent as some of the other brands I’ve tried. Overall a good option.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’ve tried probably 10 different brands of diapers. My LO always had leaks at night even when I sized up. I’m happy to say that when he wore this brand he never had any leaks! The design and fit are way different and better. I try to stick to true non-toxic brands. This one takes the cake

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Love that this product is natural. Unfortunately the cut of the diaper is very square and too wide so it doesn’t fit snuggly and causes leakage

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 7, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BEST Diapers On The Market!
reviews.reviewText: Literally the BEST diapers I have ever used! We’ve tried other brands and nothing compares to Believe! They don’t leak at all, they don’t make my daughter have a diaper rash and they are so soft and comfy. I love how they fit a bigger in size than Huggies or Pampers which makes more room for her chunky legs and tummy without having her feeling squeezed or causing leaks or diaper rash. We subscribed to a subscription via their website and got a free pack of wipes with every order. Great value for the money!! Also I love how Believe company donates diapers to families in need with every purchase. Great cause and outstanding product! Will forever be a customer!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 2, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Pee goes right through!!!
reviews.reviewText: I don’t know what it is. These diapers are NOT the move. My son has peed through them day after day. It’s not that the diaper is too full. We literally just changed him and we’re carrying him around and pee gushed right out the side. It’s something about the future around the leg is absolutely terrible! They are soft and non toxic which is great! Don’t waste your money on these! Joonya is the only non toxic diaper that seems to work for my son!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Two kids and 20 diaper brands later, I found these and they are absolute luxurious heaven. They are So Soft, lightweight but durable. No leakage yet, even when my little had diarrhea. The diapers also don’t smell either (some all natural diapers amplify the pee smell). I love that these are an all natural brand with stellar functionality. I cannot say enough positive things about them.
